column2: SELECT specObjID, bestObjID, rownum, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY rownum) as rownum2 FROM ( SELECT specObjID, bestObjID, z as rownum FROM SpecObj WHERE class = &&& AND zWarning = # AND z BETWEEN # AND # AND (survey = &&& or survey = &&&) AND bestObjID <> &&&) as t where t.rownum % #= #  order by rownum
